race.comment: TEXAS FIREBALL (3) has hit the frame in all three runs this preparation and looks to be building up to another victory. Gets 3kg off from the inside marble and should be right there at the business end. PEPPERDINE (1) has hit the top-four in all five runs this time in work and is racing very consistently of late. Should run his usual honest race. SOCIAL OUTCAST (2) got an overdue win last time and winning hoop Lerena sticks in the irons. Top-three aspirations on that form. PIERONIMO (9) strips fitter second-up from the break and maps nicely for this from the low draw. Can figure in the finish. RING BEARER (7) best of the rest with the claim.
